<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Jerusalem, khawpi thak, vak leh hawihtak ah,
 Mi thiengtho cheng chengte leh lopite a umnau a khun;
 Hukdampa chu mui ting un, A lopina chang hitiu,
 Jerusalem thak hawihtak a khun.

[V2]
 Aw Jerusalem hawihtak (2)
 Mi thiengtho cheng chengte leh lopite a umnau a khun;
 Hukdampa chuh mui ting un, A lopina chang hitiu,
 Jerusalem thak hawihtak a khun.

[V3]
 2. Aw, Jerusalem thak khuh, nawpna khawpi ahi,
 Ziechun kulhpi hawih takah kumsawta vak lopi a chun;
 Hatlohna cheng bei tan tin, chaute chu chawldam ta'n au,
 Jerusalem thak hawihtak a khun.

[V4]
 3. Aw vana Jerualem, khawpi vak leh hawih chuh,
 A lopi zie haw cheng cheng chu le hun mu ngei hiting un;
 Khawpi Sana tuol nuom chu, Belam No chun A salhvak,
 Jerusalem thak hawihtak a khun.</lyrics>
<title>JERUSALEM THE NEW CITY</title>
<hymn_number>393</hymn_number>
</song>